{"tid":2489612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超指國安法實施後很多叛國者鬧事者已退休或已逃走","createTime":"2021-04-15T05:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T06:20:15.000Z","uid":283837,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3eaf922416912bba686feef0686f5e5a2207cbfb","tid":2489612,"uid":283837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:02:21.000Z","msg":"保安局局長李家超表示，國安法實施後，本港已從2019年的動盪中回到正常生活，很多叛國者及鬧事者已宣布退休或已逃走，亦見到海外資金停止流入，制止了海外及本地組織搞事。　<br />\n<br />\n李家超接受《南華早報》訪問時說，時間愈久便愈能看清局面，外國的干預是令香港改變的其中一關鍵因素，導致香港出現暴力及殘暴的事。他表示，警方及其他紀律部隊高度戒備，一些本地人士仍然與外國勢力勾結，包括繼續在社交媒體及其他平台宣揚他們的主張。<br />\n<br />\n李家超在專訪中形容，一些逃避法律責任流亡的人是「懦夫」，與他們一直向外宣稱做正義的事，背道而馳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585885-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585885-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=786763e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1585885-20210415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=843c31de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1585885-20210415.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f8144472a0e064db6309c59cd133e7f7bd7c6ff4","tid":2489612,"uid":84176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"李蓮英局長好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c22d50ac1eb46b2fc12a2e0ccdc9e6d8bc83da3","tid":2489612,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f8144472a0e064db6309c59cd133e7f7bd7c6ff4","tid":2489612,"uid":84176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"李蓮英局長好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"今日國安法乜乜日, 要安排班撚樣出嚟打飛機俾上面睇"},{"pid":"20e3bb5437723735e5d046ec6eae4f648cb877a8","tid":2489612,"uid":179